# Skill #11 - MVC Design Pattern

Skill Demonstration Challenge

---

## Objective

Demonstrate that you can apply the MVC Pattern

Show the following details

* Apply the MVC example code from "demo/30" to "notes"
* MVC Pattern applied to notes
* Database CRUD
* Single PHP file
* Views: List, Detail, Add, Edit, Delete
* Take a screen shot of the working app



## Steps 
* Go to your dashboard page and verify your screenshots in the skill section.


## Demonstration

Each skill can be proved with a screen shot.


